name: FMN-dependent NADH-azoreductase
classes: Acting on other nitrogenous compounds as donors;
With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
comment: Requires FMN. The enzyme catalyses the reductive cleavage of an azo bond in aromatic azo compounds to form the corresponding amines. Does not accept NADPH. cf. EC 1.7.1.6, azobenzene reductase.
